name: Jade Snake Sword 玉蛇剑
description:
The body of the sword is as clear as jade, and it is curved like a snake. so is is called Jade snake sword.
剑身通体如玉一般晶莹剔透，并且弯曲如蛇，故名玉蛇剑。

name: Everspring Sabre 绣春刀
description:
The name 'Everspring' was originally the name of the Royal Park, which shows the close relationship between the Embroidered Uniform Guard and the royal family.
“绣春”一词原为皇家园名，以示锦衣卫与皇家的关系密切。

name: Sai 三叉刺
description:
Also known as the 'Pen Rack Bayonet', it is a common weapon used by the police officer of Ming Dynasty, which is easy to carry and hide on the waist.
又名“笔架叉”，衙役捕快的常用武器，易于携带，暗藏腰间。

name: Dragon Longsword 金龙长剑
description:
Ornamented by a pair of dragons from the sword hilt with golden reflection. It is called the Golden Dragon long Sword.
剑柄处双龙盘旋而上，剑身反光后泛金色，被称为金龙长剑。

name: Tiger Sabre 虎头长刀
description:
The Tiger-head Long Sabre is a kind of horse-chopping sabre and very powerful. The name 'Tiger-head' is because there is a tiger-head ornament on its hilt.
虎头长刀是斩马刀的一种，因刀柄处镶有虎头得名。

name: Xuanyuan Greatsword 轩辕重剑
description:
Though Named Xuanyuan, whether it contains infinite power that can kill the devil is unknown.
名为轩辕，但是否蕴藏无穷之力，为斩妖除魔的神剑就不得而知了。

name: Overlord Spear 霸王枪
description:
The first of the ten famous spears. It is made by the admixture of fine steel and gold. How magnificent it is!
十大名枪之首，精钢黄金混铸而成，端的是金光闪闪，霸气十足。

name: Red-tassell Spear 红缨枪
description:
Tassel dyes as the color of blood. With that blood color, it can not only increase morole, but also easily give the enemy distractions while attack.
缨穗吸血，攻击时可以给对手造成错觉，增加士气。

name: Snake Spear 丈八蛇矛
description:
The body of the spear is 10.93 inches long and the spearhead is 0.87 inches long, with blade on both edges. The spearhead shaped as a snake and therefore called Snake Spear.
矛杆长一丈，矛尖长八寸，刃开双锋，作游蛇形状，故而名之。

name: Prince Headwear 少堡主头巾
description:
A highly decorated piece of equipment, probably belonging to a high ranking personnel.
看上去就价值不菲的头巾，应是地位显赫之人的穿戴。

name: Buddha Headware 五佛冠
description:
Often worn by high ranking buddist.
五佛冠是佛教密宗上师、主持、方丈修法时，戴著像徵五智如来的宝冠。

name: Sedge hat 斗笠
description:
Sedge hat is used primarily as protection from the sun and rain, mostly made of straw or matting.
一种遮挡阳光和蔽雨的编结帽，是夹油纸或竹叶，棕丝等编织而成。

name: Swordsman Hat 剑侠帽
description:
Light and comfortable, the flexible fabric adapt all sorts of activities, suitable for martial artsist, hence the name.
质地非常轻巧舒适而且具有一定保护作用，适合习武之人穿着，故名。

name: Feather Twinswords 雀翎双剑
description:
The body of this sword as thin as the cicada's wings. It is very light weighted and well balanced, even you almost cannot feel any weight while carrying this pair of swords.
薄如蝉翼，十分轻巧，拿在手里仿佛没有重量但却锋利异常。

name: Imperial Sabre 龙阙长刀
description:
This sabre belongs to a long forgotten empire. Rumors say when this sabre shows up, fires will burn, lifes will be lost.
火从龙阙起，泪向马嵬垂。龙阙出刃必见血光，但它的来源已无迹可寻。

name: White Jade Sword 白玉双剑
description:
The body of this kind of sword is made of cold iron. Its scabbard and hilt are both made of white jade.
剑身为寒铁打造，剑鞘和剑柄均为白玉打造，同玉蛇剑齐名。

name: Eclipse Sabre 日蚀长刀
description:
The color of this sabre is so dark that even the sunlight will fade when facing it.
漆黑的刀身如吞落日之势，又如被日光吞噬，被江湖人称日蚀。

name: Blacksteel Cutlass 乌精单刀
description:
The cutlass is made of black steel. Blood shall not stain it's blade due to the special forging method.
由乌色精钢打造双刀之一的单刀，因为材质和打造过程特殊，刃不沾血。

name: Coldsteel Rapiers 寒铁双刺
description:
Dual rapiers made with coldsteel, sharp and stainless, swinging it give off a cold aura.
天山寒铁打造的双刺，锋利无比而且不会锈蚀，挥舞时仿佛带有寒气侵蚀。

name: Blacksteel Sabre 乌精长刀
description:
The sabre is made of black steel. Blood shall not stain it's blade due to the special forging method.
由乌色精钢打造双刀之一的长刀，因为材质和打造过程特殊，刃不沾血。

name: Wolf Sword 狼腾剑
description:
It is said the Wolf Sword is made by super rare steel, but no one has ever seen its true power.
狼腾剑相传由稀世钢材打造，但是没有人见过它真正的威力。

name: Phoenix Cutlass 黑凰刀
description:
The body of the sabre is made by Tamahagane, which is extremely sharp and full of tenacity. People who slashing the sabre looks like full of anger and violence.
刀身由玉刚打造，锋利无比并坚韧异常。挥舞时仿佛充斥着暴力和愤怒。

name: Hooked Cutlass 寒勾刀
description:
The Cold Hook Knife is derived from the Damascus sabre. But it has been modified to be lighter than the origin and easier penatrate enemy's armor.
寒勾刀源于大马士革刀，但是经过改良更加轻便和富有穿刺力。

name: Taoist Cap 道士冠
description:
The key feature of the Taoist Cap is to contain the long hair to accommodate training needs.
道士冠的主要作用就是将头发盘在里面方便练功。

name: Stealth Cap 夜行帽
description:
Clothing focus on infiltration and nimbleness.
与夜行衣配套的帽子，增加隐秘效果。

name: Sunglow Tiara 东方霞冠
description:
This scarlet tiara symbolizes supreme authority and power.
火红色的帽子，与东方霞衣为一套。

name: Wyrm Cap 飞鱼帽
description:
Headwear in Wyrm set for casual situation.
同飞鱼服一起搭配的帽子，用于平常走动时穿戴。

name: General's Hat 紫金飞鱼帽
description:
A symbol of high ranking officals and usually wore in formal situation.
紫金飞鱼帽主要作用是处理公务时穿戴，官位的象征。

name: Cyan Veil 隐隐青纱
description:
Silk veil of cyan color made for female.
女性专用的青色丝质面纱。

name: River Hat 黄河笠帽
description:
Plain and simple sedge hat wore by the Yellow River vagabonds.
传闻是黄河侠客所佩戴过的毡帽，朴实无华。

name: Bamboo Hat 竹斗笠
description:
Sedge hat weaved with bamboo stripes.
跟普通斗笠类似，主要是用竹条编制而成。

name: Scarlet Veil 隐隐绯纱
description:
Made with thin and opaque scarlet silk.
女性专用的绯色丝质面纱。

name: Felt Cap 毡帽
description:
Common felt cap with a rain blocking brim.
江湖常见的宽檐帽，能够挡雨。

name: Wyrm Helm 飞鱼盔
description:
Headwear in Wyrm set for operations.
同飞鱼服一起搭配的头盔，用于执行公务时穿戴。

name: General's Helm 紫金飞鱼盔
description:
Waved with thin steel threads thus offer superior protection dispite it's chiffon like appearance.
紫金飞鱼盔看似如薄纱，实则使用轻便的钢丝打造，防御力不可轻视。

name: Black Swordsman Hat 剑侠黑帽
description:
Identical with swordsman Hat only dyed black.
黑色的剑侠帽，更适合隐匿身形。

name: Guard Helmet 禁军头盔
description:
Worn by imperial guards. Invulnerable to most arrows.
禁军统领配备的头盔，一般箭矢无法伤之分毫。

name: Ghosts Cap 鬼面鳞盔
description:
Cap used by Ghost troops.
为鬼面军中将军所佩戴的头盔，主要是身份象征。

name: Bone Bow 兽骨弓
description:
Bow made from beast bones.
由兽骨制成，韧性很好，适合快速射击。

name: Jade Snake Bow 玉蛇弓
description:
Snake skin and jade made together bow, gorgeous but practical general.
蛇皮和玉器一起打造的弓身，华丽但是实用性一般。

name: Wooden Bow 杉木弓
description:
Cunninghamia lanceolata made of bow, high practicability, durable.
杉木制作的弓，实用性高，经久耐用。

name: Snakescale Bow 蛇皮弓
description:
Snake skin wrap made, toughness and durability are good, suitable for strong bow.
蛇皮包裹制作而成，韧性和耐性都很好，适合强弓。

name: TShort Crossbow 短巧弩
description:
The crossbow is short, easy to hide and used as a hidden weapon.
弩身短小，易于隐藏，被当作暗器来使用。

name: Delicate Crossbow 杉木弩
description:
Cunninghamia lanceolata made of crossbow, high practicability, durable.
杉木制作的弩，实用性高，经久耐用。

name: Eagle Crossbow 射雕弩
description:
The craft of the crossbow is complicated and named for its long range.
射雕弩的制造工艺复杂，因射程远而得名。

name: Police hat 衙役帽
description:
Daily wear of Police officers.
帽子呈四方形，戴的时候是以一个方角向前，前高后低。

name: Crate Headwear 宝箱头饰
description:
With a treasure chest on the head, funny, usually used for festival performance.
用料讲究且华丽尊贵的头冠，乃是殊荣之人才可获得的穿着。

name: Sheriff hat 捕快帽
description:
Daily wear of Sheriff.
帽子两侧缀有黄色的流苏，或插上一根鸟羽，以示身份高低。

name: Soul Spear 招魂幡
description:
Weapons used by Executor.
黑白双煞使用的武器，引幡招魂，清静魂身。

name: Clouds Sword 凌云单剑
description:
The sword is shining like a glow, it is the equipment of martial arts master.
剑出如霞，飘飘有凌云之气，似游天地之闲意。

name: Moon Miter 云锦月华发带
description:
The wearing of noble people.
云锦制成的白色发带，宛若天上云霞，乃是殊荣之人才可获得的穿着。

name: B-Executor Hat 黑煞头冠
description:
The wearing of B-Executor.
赏善罚恶使之一的黑煞，头戴黑色头冠。

name: W-Executor Hat 白煞头冠
description:
The wearing of W-Executor.
赏善罚恶使之一的白煞，头戴白色头冠。

name: Brass Hand Cannon 黄铜三眼铳
description:
Brass made of hand cannon, easy to replace gunpowder, but not durable.
黄铜制成的三眼铳，方便替换火药，但是并不耐用。

name: Black Hand Cannon 黑铁三眼铳
description:
Black iron made of hand cannon, high temperature resistance, more convenient to replace gunpowder.
黑铁制成的三眼铳，耐高温，更加方便替换火药。

name: Ivory hand cannon 象白火铳
description:
Ivory hand cannon, apart from the color, the larger ammo is its characteristic.
象白色的火铳，除了颜色，弹药较大是其特色。

name: Hand Cannon M 金环火铳
description:
Body around the gold ring, increase temperature resistance, easy to replace gunpowder.
统身金环环绕，增加耐温强度，容易更换火药。

name: Phoenix Longsword 凤凰长剑
description:
A long sword with very shinning lights is dazzling.
据说此剑剑光凌厉，出鞘之时剑光四射，耀人眼目。

name: DouYu Epee 斗鱼·鳞光重剑
description:
DouYu Special Epee.
似鳞光一般闪耀的重剑，光华耀人。

name: DouYu Hat 斗鱼·鲨浔冠
description:
DouYu Special Hat.
冠上有鱼鳞装饰，又似鲨鱼鳍一般。

name: Aspire Hat 凤求凰竖冠
description:
The wearing of Aspiring people.
用料讲究且华丽尊贵的头冠，乃是殊荣之人才可获得的穿着。

name: Rigor Hat 霜威毡帽
description:
The wearing of Martinet.
使用特殊皮料制成的毡帽，适合在寒冷的地方穿着。

name: Rigor Helmet 霜威战盔
description:
The wearing of Martinet.
使用特殊皮料制成的头盔，适合在寒冷的地方穿着。

name: Tenpo Hat 天蓬冠
description:
The wearing of Tenpo gensui.
传说天蓬元帅下凡之时穿着过的头冠，冠上有金箍装饰。

name: Tenpo Rake 九齿钉耙
description:
The weapon of Tenpo gensui.
天蓬元帅使用的武器，全名称为上宝沁金耙，相传乃太上老君用神冰铁亲自锤炼。

name: Ronin Hat 浪人斗笠
description:
Used to hide faces, also protects wearer from sun and rain.
除了掩盖面目之外，还能遮阳挡雨。

name: Su's Hat 苏夜斗笠
description:
The wearing of Su Ye Jin.
苏夜锦常戴的斗笠，虽不特殊但实用性很强。

name: MagmaFall Epee 焱瀑重剑
description:
It is like a wind-assisted fire, sparks splashing, like a flowing fire waterfall.
挥舞时似风助火势，有火花外溅，仿佛流火瀑布，故称焱瀑重剑。

name: Dragons Helmet 龙吟面甲
description:
Iron-shaped human face armor with dragon horn decoration, as if the battle of the Dragon Palace is coming.
精铁打造的人型面甲，配有龙角装饰，仿佛龙宫的战将降临。

name: Dragons Spear 龙吟长枪
description:
The silver body of the Spear, and the tour dragon circled up to the top of the Spear. When it waved, it seemed as if the tour dragon was out of the sea.
枪体银光寒芒，游龙盘旋而上至枪尖处，挥舞时犹似游龙出海一瞬般闪耀。

name: Soul's Sword 骨魂单剑
description:
Animal bones and metal mixed together to create a single sword, not only looking at terror, the damage is very high.
兽骨和金属混在一起打造出来的单剑，不仅看着恐怖，杀伤力亦不俗。

name: Hooked Cutlass 钩齿单刀
description:
The Hooked Cutlass itself is not sharp, terrible is the pain caused by the hook cut.
钩齿刀本身并不锋利，可怕的是被钩齿划破后带来的痛楚。

name: Water Cutlass 劈水单刀
description:
The body of the knife is thick and heavy, as if it could split the water temporarily, so it is named.
刀身厚重，使劲挥砍时仿佛能够将水面暂时劈开，故而得名。

name: Soul's Cutlass 骨魂单刀
description:
Animal bones and metal mixed together to create a single cutlass, not only looking at terror, the damage is very high.
兽骨和金属混在一起打造出来的单刀，不仅看着恐怖，杀伤力亦不俗。。

name: Squama Cutlass 龙鳞单刀
description:
It is not known whether it was really made of dragon scales, but the scale on the back of the cutlass is the strongest, both offensive and defensive is strong.
是否真由龙鳞打造而来不得而知，但是刀背的鳞片十分最坚固，攻守兼备。

name: FireRune Rapiers 火符双刺
description:
Blade body has runes, rune below seems to be covered by the flame of the whole body red, hence the name.
刃身有符文，符文以下似被火焰笼罩通体泛红，故名。

name: Piercingly Rapiers 冽骨双刺
description:
Rapiers made of thousands of years of cold ice and metal, sharp cruel and cold.
以千年寒冰和金属混合制成的双刺，凛冽彻骨，寒气逼人。

name: HIce flame Rapiers 冰焰双刺
description:
The craftsman of build firerune rapiers and piercingly rapiers , specially combine the two, become new Ice flame Rapiers.
打造火符双刺和冰焰双刺的工匠，特地将两者进行了结合，成为新的冰焰双刺。

name: Bamboo Longsword 青竹长剑
description:
The handle and sheath are made of the most common bamboo, carrying very light, Tibetan front in bamboo.
柄和鞘由坚韧的竹子制作，携带十分轻巧，藏剑于竹中。

name: Lute Longsword 琵琶长剑
description:
Pipa grip handle is also a sword handle, hidden sword in the body of Pipa, everywhere hidden killing opportunity.
琵琶握柄亦是剑柄，藏剑于枇杷身内，处处隐藏杀机。

name: Umbrella Longsword 千机长剑
description:
Umbrella handle is also a sword handle, by the control of the organs can freely draw out the blade, so the name of Umbrella Longsword.
伞柄又是剑柄，由机关控制可自由抽出剑刃，故名千机长剑。

name: Weepblood Sabre 泣血长刀
description:
Because too sharp, blood does not touch the blade, attached blood will quickly drop from the blade body, hence the name.
因为过于锋利，血不沾刃，附着的血液会迅速从刃身滴落，故名。

name: Brokenride Sabre 断骑长刀
description:
Like horse-chopping swords, very heavy, but also very sharp, the lack of strength can not play its real power.
隶属陌刀，十分厚重，亦很锋利，力量不足者无法发挥其真正威力。

name: Soul's Epee 骨魂重剑
description:
Animal bones and metal mixed together to create a Epee, not only looking at terror, the damage is very high.
兽骨和金属混在一起打造出来的重剑，不仅看着恐怖，杀伤力亦不俗。

name: Crescent Spear 月牙戟
description:
The crescent blade on the halberd emerged a layer of silver-covered splendor, like moonlight, hence the name.
戟上的月牙刃浮现着一层银蒙蒙的光华，仿佛月光，故而得名。

name: Soul's Spear 骨魂长枪
description:
Animal bones and metal mixed together to create a Spear, not only looking at terror, the damage is very high.
兽骨和金属混在一起打造出来的长枪，不仅看着恐怖，杀伤力亦不俗。

name: Glow Hat 耀辉笠
description:
There was a bell on the hat to remindthieves and rascals that the goods were escorted by the armed escort.
斗笠上挂有铃铛，用于提醒宵小这是有镖师押送的货物。

name: Crane's Hat 栖鹤笠
description:
At the same time with hat and mask function, light and breathable, can shelter from rain and wind.
同时具有斗笠和面罩的功能，轻便透气，可遮风挡雨。

name: Scaly Cap 蛟纹帽
description:
The hat that matches with scaly clothes, used for ordinary wear, have no special function.
同蛟纹服搭配的帽子，用于平常穿戴，没有特殊功能。

name: Zither Dual Swords 古筝双剑
description:
Playing zither at the same time, can also draw from both sides of the sword,Hidden hidden murderous in the invisible.
双手抚筝的同时，亦可从两边抽出双剑，暗藏杀机于无形。

name: Bamboo Sword 青竹单剑
description:
The handle and scabbard are made of tough bamboo, which is very lightweight and hides a sword in it.
柄和鞘由坚韧的竹子制作，携带十分轻巧，藏剑于竹中。

name: Bamboo Cutlass 青竹单刀
description:
The handle and scabbard are made of tough bamboo, which is very lightweight and hides a cutlass in it.
柄和鞘由坚韧的竹子制作，携带十分轻巧，藏刀于竹中。

name: Bamboo Dual Swords 青竹双剑
description:
The handle and scabbard are made of tough bamboo, which is very lightweight and hides a dual swords in it.
柄和鞘由坚韧的竹子制作，携带十分轻巧，藏剑于竹中。

name: Bamboo Spear 青竹长枪
description:
The spear rod is made of tough bamboo, carrying very light, hidden blade in bamboo.
枪杆由坚韧的竹子制作，携带十分轻巧，藏刃于竹中。

name: Dead wood Sword 枯木单剑
description:
Everything can be a sword, although it is dead wood, but hurt in the invisible, can not be underestimated.
万物皆可为剑，虽是枯木，却伤人于无形，不可小觑。
